  h1 My Projects
  p I love writing code. Below you'll find information about projects I've worked on.
  .project
    h2 Carbon Nation Alpha
    p Carbon Nation is a game about a guy seeking revenge against homeland intruders. This version of the game is a prototype for the planned mobile release. This prototype is written in Javascript and WebGL and was created during CS452 at Clarkson University.
    a(href="https://github.com/hunterdquant/CarbonNationAlpha")
      button(type="button", class="source-button btn btn-lg", name="button") Source
  .project
    h2 Beat Blocks Alpha
    p Beat Blocks is a rhythm-puzzle game for the Android platform. This game was made during CS242 at Clarkson University. The game was written in Java using the standard Android SDK.
    a(href="https://github.com/hunterdquant/BeatBlocksAlpha")
      button(type="button", class="source-button btn btn-lg", name="button") Source
  .project
