      button(type="button", class="source-button btn btn-lg", name="button") Source
  .project
    h2 RotateJS
    p RotateJS is a Javascript API designed to make it easy for people to rotate images and videos on a cube.
    a(href="https://github.com/hunterdquant/RotateJS")
      button(type="button", class="source-button btn btn-lg", name="button") Source
